Today, The British Publishing Company consists of full-time reporters, data journalism specialists, researchers and editors.Â  Our team have spent years undertaking investigative reports with organisations such as The Times, FT, The Washington Post, Forbes and Time magazine.Â  Between us, we have a vast level of experience of national and local print, radio, television, online, social platforms and new media.

We are not a business that is trying to revolutionize the world. We simply develop great ideas for cutting edge digital campaigns, publications, and events which connect our clients to key influences and customers within their sector and thatâ€™s about it.

